description: Colorful and lively character illustrations featuring large eyes and exaggerated expressions.
8-bit retro game style artwork composed of pixelated dots, featuring characters and landscapes.
Soft and translucent watercolor style illustrations, featuring natural landscapes, flowers, and animals, conveying a gentle and calm impression.
Simple yet profound monochrome sketch style, suitable for cityscapes, portraits, and abstract designs, offering a chic and artistic icon.
Photo style with vintage processing that evokes the atmosphere of the good old days, with faded colors and film texture bringing a nostalgic impression to the icon.
